  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>Allocated on Arrival - 7 nights - Self catering</strong></p>
<p><br />These well located 2 and 3 star apartments offer excellent value accommodation in this high altitude resort. The all offer skiing from the doorstep and are either located right in the centre of the Three Valleys Ski Area or within an easy 5 minutes' walk. Each apartment sleeps 2-5 people and has cooking facilities, a bath/shower roomand a balcony or terrace. You will be allocated  accommodation to suit your party size.</p>]]></description>
