  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Studios for 2-4 people have either a double or 2 single sofa beds and bunk beds in a cabin area.</li>
<li>2-room apartments have 2 single sofa beds and a pull-out bed plus a separate bedroom with a double bed.</li>
<li>All have bath or shower room with WC and most have a balcony or terrace.</li>
<li>Bed linen and local taxes are included in the price. Towels are available locally (approx €7 per set)</li>
<li>Refundable deposit of €300 (approx) payable on arrival</li>
<li>Credit cards accepted</li>
<li>Return airport transfers are included but may be to a central point from where you may need to take a local taxi (fare not included) to your allocated accommodation</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
